CREATED:20260128T182324Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260128T182325Z
UID:10001459-1775585700-1775590200@ncwf.org
SUMMARY:Water Features for Wildlife (Concord)
DESCRIPTION:We all know that wildlife needs food\, water\, shelter\, and places to raise young. We also know that pests need the same. How do we reach a balance? Join Concord Wildlife Alliance as we welcome Tracy LeCompte from Cooperative Extension for a conversation about how to incorporate water into your backyard habitat. \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/water-features-for-wildlife-concord/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/waterhello.jpg
END:VEVENT
