SUMMARY:Conservation Equipment Day (Monroe)
DESCRIPTION:Join landowners and natural resource staff as we explore equipment options\, management techniques\, and professional assistance available to help you meet your conservation goals for your property! Participants will have the opportunity to operate equipment with an instructor and converse with a variety of forestry and wildlife professionals. \nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://ncwf.org/event/conservation-equipment-day-monroe/
CATEGORIES:Featured
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ncwf.org/wp-content/uploads/Conservation-Equipment-Field-Day-Flyer-scaled.jpg
