SUMMARY:Holding Park Garden Workday (Wake Forest)
DESCRIPTION:Join NCWF Neuse River Hawks Conservationists Chapter for a garden workday at Holding Park in Wake Forest. Volunteers will help pull weeds and add botanical labels to the native plants in the garden. Come lend a hand! \nREGISTER HERE
