SUMMARY:Urban Treen Planting (Charlotte)
DESCRIPTION:A total of 95 trees will be planted at two city properties to improve tree canopy coverage. Trees provide shade\, reduce ambient heat\, create wildlife habitat\, and enhance community greenspaces. And you can help plant them! \nREGISTER HERE
